":[{"content":"Read issue context and determine requested ontology change","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Perform required term search, design-pattern review, and research if needed","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Validate current ontology state before edits","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Make scoped ontology edits via checkout/checkin workflow","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run post-change validation","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Commit only intended edited files","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Create ISSUE_COMMENTS.md and PR_COMMENTS.md without committing them","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"6 todos","time":{"start":1778981645001,"end":1778981645008}},"id":"prt_e3391a3b3001H1xX1KF8Tm3o42","sessionID":"ses_1cc6e9e73ffe2HfOe2xPGj0ykX","messageID":"msg_e33918f35001OJw0p0C8J6QjdT"}}
{"type":"text","timestamp":1778981645034,"sessionID":"ses_1cc6e9e73ffe2HfOe2xPGj0ykX","part":{"id":"prt_e33919f59001a8zSY9q68OUQ8o","messageID":"msg_e33918f35001OJw0p0C8J6QjdT","sessionID":"ses_1cc6e9e73ffe2HfOe2xPGj0ykX","type":"text","text":"The issue is clear enough to implement: add the specific ferric iron reductase activity term, reclassify `GO:0000293`, and correct its chelate-based definition. Next I’m checking existing ontology patterns, reaction guidance, and literature-backed references before editing.","time":{"start":1778981642073,"end":1778981645032}}}
