{"type":"text","timestamp":1778982281911,"sessionID":"ses_1cc6e9e73ffe2HfOe2xPGj0ykX","part":{"id":"prt_e339b4e6d001e7fegMfHOT0Qol","messageID":"msg_e339b48580016kwzNInvXGipkS","sessionID":"ses_1cc6e9e73ffe2HfOe2xPGj0ykX","type":"text","text":"Implemented and committed the ontology change for issue `#27593`.\n\nWhat changed:\n- Added new term `GO:7770068` `ferric iron reductase activity`\n- Reparented `GO:0000293` `ferric-chelate reductase activity` under the new term\n- Corrected the `GO:0000293` definition from siderophore-specific wording to broader chelate wording on both sides of the reaction\n- Added `RHEA:71767` and requested PMID xrefs/provenance to the new term\n\nValidation:\n- Pre-edit SPARQL validation passed\n- Post-edit SPARQL validation passed\n- ELK reasoning passed\n- PMID support text in `RESEARCH.md` validated with `linkml-reference-validator`\n\nCommit:\n- Local commit created: `377edf4` with message `Add ferric iron reductase activity term`\n\nFiles created for handoff and left uncommitted:\n- `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md`\n- `PR_COMMENTS.md`\n\nSupporting local docs also created and left uncommitted:\n- `RESEARCH.md`\n- `DESIGN_PATTERNS.md`\n\nImportant note:\n- The issue thread previously mentioned `GO:7770057`, but that ID is already occupied in this evaluation checkout, so I used the next free local ID `GO:7770068`.","time":{"start":1778982276717,"end":1778982281909}}}
